OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774703465
OL,3,CPortadown murder victim named as
OL,4,CRolandas Kvederis
OL,6,FA man murdered in Co Armagh has been
OL,7,Fnamed by police as 49-year-old
OL,8,FRolandas Kvederis.
OL,10,FTwo men are still being questioned
OL,11,Ffollowing the death of Mr Kvederis in
OL,12,FPortadown on Thursday.
OL,14,FA PSNI spokesperson said they received
OL,15,Fa report of an altercation at a
OL,16,Fproperty in the Ranfurley Road area
OL,17,Fshortly after 11pm and attended with
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland Ambulance Service
OL,19,Fcolleagues.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
