OL,3,CPortadown murder victim named as
OL,4,CRolandas Kvederis
OL,6,FThey added: "Sadly, Mr Kvederis was
OL,7,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,9,F"Two men aged in their 50s were
OL,10,Farrested on suspicion of murder and
OL,11,Fremain in police custody."
OL,13,FPolice have appealed to anyone who
OL,14,Fbelieves they may have information to
OL,15,Fcontact them.
